description: Gameday Grill is a mobile food truck in the Sacramento area specializing in grilled items.  Featuring their signature Puerto Rican Plate (with Puerto Rican style yellow rice & beans),  Gameday Grill offers many grilled to order items. Meat choices include Tri-tip, grilled Chicken Breast, and gourmet Burgers, and all items can be purchased a la carte or as a combo. Only at Gameday!! "Where we GRILL to order."
name: Gameday Grill
